00:43:36.330 --> 00:43:41.040
And that was not just part
of their early upbringing

00:43:41.040 --> 00:43:43.680
and subsistence, it was
part of community building.

00:43:43.680 --> 00:43:45.660
And it was part of
like homesteading.

00:43:45.660 --> 00:43:47.830
It is just what you
