happened in Flint, Michigan,

00:45:47.346 --> 00:45:48.720
part of the problem
there is when

00:45:48.720 --> 00:45:51.330
you have people who are not
scientists being the people who

00:45:51.330 --> 00:45:53.610
get to make a decision about
what happens to the water

00:45:53.610 --> 00:45:55.170
supply in a city.

00:45:55.170 --> 00:45:58.800
