certain age and a certain race,

00:49:26.890 --> 00:49:28.870
then of course they're
going to only reach out

00:49:28.870 --> 00:49:30.700
to the people who are--

00:49:30.700 --> 00:49:32.680
or they're going to have
a natural inclination

00:49:32.680 --> 00:49:34.054
where those people
gather and how

00:49:34.054 --> 00:49:37.930
to outreach the people who are
the same demographic as them.

00:49:37.930 --> 00:49:41.320
So as with most
things in life, it's

00:49:41.320 --> 00:49:43.720
a top down diversity issue.

00:49:43.720 --> 00:49:46.840
So if everyone in
that city office

00:49:46.840 --> 00:49:50.440
is middle aged and white,
then it's really no surprise

00:49:50.440 --> 00:49:52.060
that everyone who
