00:53:45.410 --> 00:53:50.630
guiding spatial remaking efforts
in your stories or especially

00:53:50.630 --> 00:53:51.690
with your LA project.

00:53:51.690 --> 00:53:56.570
So you talked about Central
Avenue and the highways.

00:53:56.570 --> 00:54:01.110
And so I see these changes,
these mid-century era changes

00:54:01.110 --> 00:54:04.700
